WEBVTT

00:12:00.649 --> 00:12:03.785
Martin Luther King
had just been assassinated.

00:12:04.443 --> 00:12:08.580
His maid, "domestic" --
we'll call her "Mabel,"

00:12:08.604 --> 00:12:09.809
was in the kitchen.

00:12:10.706 --> 00:12:12.312
Little Fred is eight years old.

00:12:12.336 --> 00:12:14.177
Little Fred comes into the kitchen,

00:12:14.968 --> 00:12:21.119
and Mabel, who he has only seen
as smiling and helpful and happy,

00:12:21.143 --> 00:12:23.425
is bent over the sink,

00:12:23.449 --> 00:12:24.859
and she's crying,

00:12:25.896 --> 00:12:27.311
and she's sobbing

00:12:28.479 --> 00:12:29.684
inconsolably.